# page.tsx requirements

This is a **Server Component**. Never add `'use client'` here — push interactivity
into `calculator.tsx`.

## Metadata (`export const metadata` or `generateMetadata`)
- `title`: `"<Tool> - <benefit> | Calculatories"`. Keep `<title>` and `og:title` consistent.
- `description`: unique, ~140–160 chars, contains the primary keyword.
- `alternates.canonical`: `` `${SITE_URL}${path}` `` — non-www, no trailing slash.
- `openGraph`: `title`, `description`, `url`, `images: [\`${SITE_URL}/og/<slug>.png\`]`.
  Verify the OG image file actually exists, or generate it dynamically with
  `next/og` (`opengraph-image.tsx`) so links never 404.
- `twitter`: **MUST be set per page** (`card: 'summary_large_image'`, `title`,
  `description`, `images`). Do NOT let pages inherit the homepage Twitter defaults —
  this is a known bug to avoid.

## JSON-LD (inject via `<script type="application/ld+json">`)
- `WebApplication`/`SoftwareApplication`: `name`, `description`,
  `applicationCategory`, `offers` with `price: "0"`.
- `FAQPage`: `acceptedAnswer.text` MUST be fully populated with the real answer text,
  mirroring `content.tsx` exactly. Empty/missing answers = no rich result and looks
  like thin content.
- `BreadcrumbList`: Home > Category > Tool.

## Layout
- Calculator widget above the fold, immediately after the H1.
- `<HeaderAd/>` after the H1, `<InContentAd/>` mid-content, `<SidebarAd/>` in the aside.
- Render the client `<Calculator/>` and the server `<Content/>`.
- One H1 only; section headings as H2/H3.
